text:
Airbus Singapore Training Base,
Jointly funded by Airbus Group and Singapore Airlines,
Singapore Airlines produces simulator equipment.
It opened on April 18, 2016, with new equipment and good lighting.
The gate guards are friendly and taxis can drive directly into the atrium.
Meals are not currently available, so if you want to eat you must take a taxi and eat outside.
The waiting time for a taxi is about 5 to 7 minutes.
